name: Baby doll
greetingText: ISSKE BAAD SRIF PADHAI HONI CHAIYE!
wishText: Diwale baala tu kuthe chaala? Ja tu tar already ushira aala You don't even love me, kasl re kami? Saangu ka mummy la, tu banto shaana! Maajhi saasu tujhi mother Ae maajhi honari humsafar I like your beauty, I like your fashion Tujhyavar thambun hai maajhi nazar Ek number, tujhi kambar Haay chaal shaky shaky Haay kiti sundar tujha dimple Je paahije te ghe, take it take it! Ek number, tujhi kamar Haay chaal shaky shaky Haaye kiti sundar tujha dimple Je paahije te ghe, take it take it!
